This data set has 2+ Million reviews and ratings from Amazon on Beauty related products. 
We can download this dataset from Kaggle. 
In this project this dataset is used for Popularity based and Collaborative Filtering as this have the UserId and their Product Ratings.

https://www.kaggle.com/skillsmuggler/amazon-ratings?select=ratings_Beauty.csv

This is Amazon's Original Dataset which includes various categories like Electronics, Beauty, Toys, Health and Personal Care.
Beauty Dataset is used for Content Based and Hybrid Flitering.
This Dataset includes additional features about the product including Description, Title, Asin number, Product Image.

http://jmcauley.ucsd.edu/data/amazon/
